#encoding: utf-8

Feature: Literals5 - Float

  Scenario: [1] Return a short positive float
    Given any graph
    When executing query:
      """
      RETURN 1.0 AS literal
      """
    Then the result should be, in any order:
      | literal |
      | 1.0     |
    And no side effects

